  "narrative_arc": "Heroin addict whose arc across all five seasons is the most complete addiction-recovery-relapse-recovery narrative in television. Simon documents every institutional encounter — the rehab that doesn't work, the homelessness between relapses, the police who use him as an informant, and ultimately the NA meeting and the sister's house that save him.",
